FORMAT: 1A
HOST: http://localhost:3000/api

# Library Management API

API quản lý thư viện - Demo API Blueprint format.

## Books Collection [/books]

### Lấy danh sách sách [GET]

+ Parameters
    + search (string, optional) - Tìm kiếm theo tên hoặc tác giả
    + genre (string, optional) - Lọc theo thể loại

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        [
            {
                "id": 1,
                "title": "Clean Code",
                "author": "Robert C. Martin",
                "year": 2008,
                "genre": "Technology",
                "available": true
            }
        ]

### Thêm sách mới [POST]

+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "title": "Clean Code",
            "author": "Robert C. Martin",
            "year": 2008,
            "genre": "Technology"
        }

+ Response 201 (application/json)

        {
            "id": 1,
            "title": "Clean Code",
            "author": "Robert C. Martin",
            "year": 2008,
            "genre": "Technology",
            "available": true
        }

+ Response 400 (application/json)

        {
            "message": "title và author là bắt buộc"
        }

## Book [/books/{id}]

+ Parameters
    + id (number, required) - ID của cuốn sách

### Lấy sách theo ID [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
            "id": 1,
            "title": "Clean Code",
            "author": "Robert C. Martin",
            "year": 2008,
            "genre": "Technology",
            "available": true
        }

+ Response 404 (application/json)

        {
            "message": "Resource not found"
        }

### Cập nhật sách [PUT]

+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "title": "Clean Code 2nd Edition",
            "author": "Robert C. Martin",
            "year": 2024,
            "genre": "Technology"
        }

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
            "id": 1,
            "title": "Clean Code 2nd Edition",
            "author": "Robert C. Martin",
            "year": 2024,
            "genre": "Technology",
            "available": true
        }

### Xóa sách [DELETE]

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
            "message": "Xóa thành công"
        }

+ Response 404 (application/json)

        {
            "message": "Resource not found"
        }